=========================

For using Auto Scaling Group purpose is if we have some servers and CPU Threshold limit has 60% that CPU utilization Threshold limit has crossed means automatically one servers has be 
to get created for this purpose we will use Auto Scaling Group

How to create this Auto SCaling Group is like below

In k8s if Pod has got deleted means again new POD will get created from a template 
